                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a shoemaker; I have known him sixteen or seventeen years, a very good man, what I always thought, I knew his wife perfectly well, I have seen them frequently together, in the manner which they lived, they appeared to me to live on friendly and good terms as far as ever I saw.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860426-42-person635">
                  EDWARD
                   CHIPPER
