                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I live in Leadenhall-market; I have known him five years, I never knew any thing amiss of him, a good-natured inoffensive man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860426-42-person636">
                  GEORGE
                   PACKWOOD
               <interp inst="t17860426-42-person636" type="surname" value="PACKWOOD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860426-42-person636" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>
