                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I live in Gracechurch-street; I am a hair-dresser, and perfumer; I knew him ten or eleven years; I knew his wife well, I look upon it in my opinion, he was a<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178604260100"></xptr> man of tender feelings, and a good natured man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860426-42-person637">
                  WILLIAM
                   BARNARD
               <interp inst="t17860426-42-person637" type="surname" value="BARNARD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860426-42-person637" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860426-42-person637" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
